## Reactions

```ts
await im.messages.setReaction(chat, messageGuid, { kind: "love" }, true);
await im.messages.setReaction(chat, messageGuid, { kind: "like" }, true, { partIndex: 1 });

// Emoji reaction (iOS 17+)
await im.messages.setReaction(chat, messageGuid, { kind: "emoji", emoji: "🔥" }, true);

// Remove a tapback
await im.messages.setReaction(chat, messageGuid, { kind: "love" }, false);
```

## Edit & unsend

```ts
// Edit text (iOS 16+)
await im.messages.edit(chat, messageGuid, "Corrected text", {
  backwardCompatText: "Edited: Corrected text",
  partIndex: 0,
});

// Retract a message (iOS 16+)
await im.messages.unsend(chat, messageGuid, { partIndex: 0 });
```

## Querying messages

### Get a single message

```ts
const message = await im.messages.get(chat, messageGuid);
```

### List recent messages

```ts
const page = await im.messages.listRecent({ pageSize: 25 });
page.messages;
page.nextPageToken;
```

### List messages in a chat

```ts
const page2 = await im.messages.listInChat(chat, { pageSize: 25 });
page2.messages;
page2.nextPageToken;
```

{% set listOpts = symbol("ts:@photon-ai/advanced-imessage#MessageListFilter") %}

